name: Kozzel_Qwok
content:
Kozzel Qwok was a male Pacithhip, who worked as a smuggler during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
Qwok was the leader of a Pacithhip smuggling gang and flew the modified Corellian freighter Neebray Manta. During the time of the Clone Wars, the Republic suspected Qwok and his gang of having links to the Confederacy of Independent Systems, so they spent several months trying to find him.
